			<h3>Goals:</h3>
				<p>The goals of the study group should be flexible to meet the needs of those attending.  I think a basic outline
				of goals should look something like this:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>R basics: input, output</li>
			    	<li>Data Management and Manipulation</li>
    				<li>Basic Statistics</li>
    				<li>Statistical Graphics</li>
    				<li>Basic Linear and Logistic Regressions</li>
				</ul>
